com.complexible.common.io
Interface IOFile

All Superinterfaces:
ByteReader, ByteWriter, Closeable, Flushable
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractFile, ChannelFile, DiskFile, MemFile, MMapFile
public interface IOFile
extends ByteReader, ByteWriter, Closeable, Flushable

An IOFile represents an element that supports several IO operations, depending on its IOFile.Mode.

Since:
0.3
Version:

Author:
